   =============================================================================
   変数:
     product_type_name : "ミラーレスカメラ" or "交換レンズ"
     product_type      : "ML" or "LENS"
     failure_codes     : list of {code, name, description, record_type, decision_rule}
     special_codes     : {other_code: "M046", unk_code: "M_UNK"}
